{"tid":27292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇非波台人好欣賞波台文化？","createTime":"2016-12-07T08:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T02:29:00.000Z","uid":5600,"like":15,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77fcbe49469ae6d8fb81e184aa1fa6adbf6f0f2a","tid":27292,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"波台(舊高登)學識既人都好高,低調,又不喜愛網上世界打飛機<br />\n喜愛9UP但言談中可以能言善語地講到道理<br />\n不盲目追隨高登文化如巴絲打稱呼<br />\n破舊立新堅持另類高登文化<br />\n將香港其他論壇既好處引入波台從而打進高登<br />\n獨愛男性化既運動如足球及冰壺(藍波唔計)<br />\n既不像CC台政治宅同動物台三次元毒燃<br />\n又不像潮流台同感情台咁MK<br />\n更加唔好講上班台個班90後同自怨自埋失敗者<br />\n平時波台大家有時會互串下增進感情<br />\n一有大事發生就無論英超各隊定西甲圍爐聯賽都團結起來對抗外敵(NBA唔計,死返玩具台OR黑窿)<br />\n黎得波台既大家都係好兄弟<br />\n有福同享有難同當"},{"pid":"69e4e8649faafd380942dc83595b6544ccb08f0c","tid":27292,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"打格"},{"pid":"7f65e6c03aef39c1ba8e5a95e6e715f43bc945d4","tid":27292,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:53:21.000Z","msg":"十卜打格baby"},{"pid":"7a344272604be4ce63653fd29843a24e6750baaf","tid":27292,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eacfc62b5797458d5e058c2a9c2d7ef068d6336","tid":27292,"uid":12027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"仲會一齊落老蘭🤘🏿"},{"pid":"f8bfc60b411b31d7036723e3150126e731d570c8","tid":27292,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"波台成班五毛上哂list<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a1edfb10635216766452b827ae4909009b12c3","tid":27292,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"傾慕左班波台手足好耐 典加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d32f1b0f8f9769ef0610cf843c8a4d7b798db21","tid":27292,